    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi. Anno nativitatis eius millesimo
                        centesimo trigesimo septimo, <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/51"
                            >Innocentii</persName> pape septimo, <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/3578">Lotarii</persName> imperatoris anno quarto, die
                        vigesimo septimo mensis marcii, indictione XV, iuxta <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches">Sancti Clementis</orgName>. Quia petivi a te domno
                        … <rs key="#Monks">monacho</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Poultry #Coloni/tenants #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie in <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Pomposia</placeName></orgName> ex iussione … <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abbatis</rs> tui, concesisti et largisti … pro me et pro
                        meis filiis masculis sub potestate Dominici … <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants"><name ref="Marinus">Marini</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Coloni/tenants"><name ref="Petronia"
                            >Petronie</name></persName> uxoris eius in usufructu quousque … usque ad
                        annos viginti et novem ad renovandum. Ita … debeamus rem inferius dicendam,
                        idest hoc quod predictum est … et detinet in <placeName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Poultry #Coloni/tenants"
                            ref="#places/4848">Podio</placeName>, <rs key="#Plebs">plebe</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/3626">Sancti
                            Pancracii</orgName>, scilicet … prefati monasterii tui. Sub <rs
                            key="#Levies">terratico</rs> de <rs key="#Wine">vino</rs> anforam
                        terciam, de <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores">labore [maiore]</rs> quintum, <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Minores">minuto</rs> vero octavum … <rs key="#Poultry"
                            >gallinam</rs> … deducta omni iusticia donica per nos <rs
                            key="#Coloni/tenants">colonos</rs> usque ad … Sancti Stefani. Pro eo
                        quia do tibi solidos quinque monete Lucensis. Et tu supradictus locatorum
                        abbate et monachis omnia … et defensare promisisti mihi Iohanni et meis
                        filiis scilicet masculis ab omni homine qualiter superius legitur. Ita ut
                        nos coloni … vobis … superius dictam … firma hec peticio. … peticionem
                        scripsi et complevi. Testes …</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
